name: Leek and mushroom stuffing
ingredients:
- Leek: 1 large or 2 medium, sliced
- Mushrooms: a box, quartered
- Salt, White Pepper, Black pepper:
- Tarragon, Sage, Rosemary:
steps:
- Wash and prepare ingredients
- Put pan on a low/medium heat. Add some oil, add all ingredients and slowly sweat ingredients. Stir occasionally
- After 10/15 minutes everything should be well combined and cooked thru. Moisture should have been lost in the cooking process
- Put to one side to use later or use a stuffing immediately
